  "DBA & Trademark":"Review the DBA and Trademark pages — DBA filing levels (state vs county), name/logo/slogan as separate trademarks, and that a trademark doesn't authorize local operation.",
  "Annual Report & Compliance":"Go back over the Annual Report pages by state — it's compliance not tax, the Texas two-filing rule and $2.47M block, the Delaware share-tax schedule, and Florida's late-fee rules.",
  "Dissolution, Reinstatement & Good Standing":"Review Dissolution, Reinstatement and COGS — voluntary vs administrative status, the 12 reinstatement states, COGS requirements, and reinstate-before-dissolve.",
  "Foreign Qualification":"Re-read the Foreign Qualification page — the COGS-then-file order, the DBA fix when a name is taken, and that withdrawal and domestication aren't offered by Bizee.",
  "Pricing & Packages":"Review the product pricing tables — Annual Report $129/$99, the $199 vs $99 filing fees, Business Contract Templates $150 / included with Premium, and the Formation Kit add-on rules.",
